issue.title: Better music?
issue.body:
The music I wrote for this was something I hacked together in an hour. I personally find it kindof irritating now (maybe cause Ive heard it so many times now lol). 

Maybe we can look into making something more interesting for the music...

issue.title: FR: Portrait mode
issue.body: With slight change of viewing angle, this game could easily be pushed into portrait mode, allowing easier Messenger gameplay.

issue.title: Joystick as an option
issue.body:
Some users have pointed out that it is difficult to touch the screen on phones, and they asked for a joystick to control the Runner. 

@HighPriestCthulhu is working on this in PR #2

issue.title: FR: Leaderboard/High Score
issue.body:
Use FB's 'custom_update_template' to track user's scores. 
See the bottom of the [quick start doc](https://developers.facebook.com/docs/games/instant-games/getting-started/quickstart)
